ing time at home played a key role in her decision.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9749978072256281, \"rank\": 0.02518387044815112, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999907172426652, \"rank\": 8.891348729638626e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kenny\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"her husband\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"Sir Jason\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"a second son\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"their family\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"spending time\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 576}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"a key role\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's been in my head a little while, the sacrifices of leaving the children and your family at home is really quite big and it really is a big decision to make,' Kenny said.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"the sacrifices\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"the children\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"your family\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"a big decision\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"Kenny\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sorry, this video is not available any more.\", \"from\": 797, 